# File List
- All Director-Actor relationships.gexf
- Top-20_Network Analysis.gexf
- Top-20.tiff
- combined.csv

# File Description
- All Director-Actor relationships.gexf: File created during RStudio analysis including all relationships with directors and top 15 billed cast memebers. 
- Top-20_Network Analysis.gexf: File used to create Top-20.tiff in Geophi Lite.  
- Top-20.tiff: Image of top 20 director-actor collaboration used in conference poster.
- combined.csv: This file was created during the RStudio analysis. 

# Data Specific Information
- GEXF files can be uploaded into Gephi Lite to view analysis independently. 
- All Director-Actor relationships.gexf was directly exported from RStudio Analysis.
- Top-20_Network Analysis.gexf, used created by converting combined.csv to GEXF using Table2Net website, https://medialab.github.io/table2net/  

